But what I want to do next is I'm going to take this repository I just created, and I'm going to pull it into Posit Workbench as an RStudio project.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:50.000
And to do that, the first thing I need to do is just grab the URL for this GitHub repository.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:53.000
So let me navigate over to Posit Workbench.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:58.000
And if this is the first time you're seeing Posit Workbench, this is the home screen when you first log in.

