00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:57.000
And when you click on that option, you'll get this pop-up menu to select how you want to create your project.

00:07:57.000 --> 00:08:04.000
You can create a new directory, which is like creating a new file on your desktop or your computer, for example.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:09.000
You can also create a project in an existing directory if that file already exists on your computer.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:12.000
Or you can pull in a project from Version Control.

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:15.000
And this is the option I want to use.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:19.000
Since we're using Git and GitHub, I'm going to select Git.

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:23.000
